          <p class="text-sm text-[rgb(var(--color-text-muted))]">This is muted text, typically used for secondary information, metadata, or less important content.</p>
          <p class="text-lg text-[rgb(var(--color-accent))]">This is accent colored text, used for links and secondary actions.</p>
